import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='rate', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['rate'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['rate'].mean():.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['rate'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['rate'].median():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of obesity rates across all states?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Obesity Rate')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    ax = sns.barplot(x="region", y="rate", data=data, ci=None, palette="muted")
    ax.axhline(y=data['rate'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Mean Obesity Rate')
    ax.set(xlabel='Region', ylabel='Obesity Rate')
    ax.legend(loc='upper right')
    plt.xticks(rotation=0)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
    ax = sns.barplot(x="state", y="rate", data=data, palette="Blues_d")
    ax.axhline(data['rate'].max(), ls='--', color='red', label='Max rate: {:.2f}'.format(data['rate'].max()))
    ax.axhline(data['rate'].min(), ls='--', color='green', label='Min rate: {:.2f}'.format(data['rate'].min()))
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    plt.xlabel('State')
    plt.ylabel('Obesity Rate')
    plt.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.boxplot(x="color", y="rate", data=data, ax=ax)
    ax.set_xlabel("Color")
    ax.set_ylabel("Obesity Rate")
    ax.set_title("Is there a difference in obesity rates between states with different colors?", wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
